<p>
Yesterday...
<blockquote><a href="http://m.ktvu.com/news/news/local/da-no-charges-lopez-deputy-involved-shooting/ngZ9t/"><b>Protestors march following DA's announcement of no charges in Andy Lopez case</b></a><br>
