<i>Pelosi explained, "We are all Americans -- north and south in this hemisphere," and urged America to see this as not a crisis but an opportunity "to be helpful." <b>She also said she wished she could simply "take home" the thousands of children temporarily housed in the overburden facilities</b>.</i></blockquote>
Excellent. I think she should put her <a href="http://www.celebritynetworth.com/richest-politicians/democrats/nancy-pelosi-net-worth/">estimated $100 million</a> where her socialist mouth is.
<p>
Adopt 'em, bitch.
